    {
      "id": "wanxing_farewell_2",
      "text": "路上小心，夜里的山路要小心。$[PLAYER_NAME]。",
      "favor_min": 0,
      "favor_max": 999,
      "season": "",
      "time_of_day": "",
      "weather": "",
      "heart_min": 0,
      "heart_max": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "wanxing_farewell_3",
      "text": "你走了……我会继续数星星的。但这次，数着数着就在想你了。$[PLAYER_NAME]。",
